Try to separate the files as much as possible. Create each widget, enum and class in a separate file, and use appropiate folder strucutre. 

## UI
Each widget has a separate file. The views have a base class. There's a folder /widgets inside of each major view, with the separate files for each widget of the view.
New widgets that are similar or the same than existing widgets should be abstracted to reuse code if possible. 
Common widgets are in the /shared folder.

## Logic
Each class should perform only one action. Separate the concerns as much as possible and separate everything in files with a structured folder structure.
